		<div class="module-heading ">
			<span class="brand-news-tx">Ekonomika</span>
		</div><div class="row">
			<div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
			<article class="thumbnail brand-news-hov normal wide md--large sm--large"><figure><a class="thumbnail__image lazy" data-original="https://static.lsm.lv/media/2020/02/thumbnail/1/cmod.jpg" href="/raksts/zinas/ekonomika/aicina-pasazieru-vilcienu-pieteikties-es-finansejumam-vilcienu-iegadei.a390396/"></a><div class="thumbnail__details"></div></figure><figcaption class="brand-news-br"><a class="thumbnail__caption" href="/raksts/zinas/ekonomika/aicina-pasazieru-vilcienu-pieteikties-es-finansejumam-vilcienu-iegadei.a390396/">Aicina «Pasažieru vilcienu» pieteikties ES finansējumam vilcienu iegādei</a></figcaption></article>		</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
